title: Evan McMullin
added: In October 2021, McMullin began a campaign for the [[United States Senate]], running against incumbent [[Mike Lee (American politician)|Mike Lee]] in the [[2022 United States Senate election in Utah|2022 election]].<ref name="05oct21 politico"/>
